Author: beebeelion
Text: Mine are all clear on the bottoms/tops of my front teeth, and I have some chips too. :(  I have to get bonding to fix it, but I haven't been able to afford it yet.  Totally hate smiling, and I used to be complimented on my smile all the time.

Author: trashy_panda
Text: I feel like a lot of people don't understand how important this really is. I used to have nice teeth... now I have really nice dental bills.
